  "page": "Seven Drunken Oarsmen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Seven Drunken Oarsmen</b></i> is a mummers play.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Drunken_Oarsmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Drunken_Oarsmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The mummers of <a href=\"/index.php/The_Ship\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Ship\">the Ship</a> intend to put on a performance of the <i>Seven Drunken Oarsmen</i> as an answer to the <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Lantern\" title=\"Blue Lantern\">Blue Lantern</a>'s performance of  <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lord_of_the_Woeful_Countenance\" title=\"The Lord of the Woeful Countenance\">The Lord of the Woeful Countenance</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Seven_Drunken_Oarsmen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n